text.section:
All licenses issued under this subsection shall be signed by the chairman and the secretary of the board, under the seal of the board. Each license shall bear the full name of the licensee, the license number, and one (1) of the following designations:
"Professional Engineer";
"Professional Land Surveyor";
"Professional Engineer, Inactive";
"Professional Engineer, Retired";
"Professional Land Surveyor, Inactive"; or
"Professional Land Surveyor, Retired."
